snippet.title: Onsen Master Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
As revealed during Guerrilla Collective 2021, take a fresh new look at Onsen Master, a hot spring customer management game where players must create ingredients to match the various customer ailments, across the fantasy island of Izajima.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
